Pressure sensation became more frequent--once a day for the past week , and now radiates to left arm. No n/v/f/c/orthopnea/doe. At baseline , has short walking tolerance. MIBI showed sm. amt. of inferolateral reversible ischemia , sum stress score 4 ( 4-8 mild abnl ) , and on echo , there is hypokinesis of inferolateral wall. LV is dilated , EF 45%.
